      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_01_02-koh014.m4a",
      "text": "ははは、すみません。奥山さんはずっと\n今の奥山さんのままでいて欲しいなって",
      "translations": {
